- **Channel Format**: `databases.{dbId}.collections.{colId}.documents` listens to all document CRUD events. `buckets.{bucketId}.files` listens to file uploads/deletes.
- **Event Batching**: Appwrite may send multiple events in a single callback. Always iterate `response.events`.
- **Permissions**: Realtime respects your collection/bucket permissions. Users will only receive events for resources they have `read` access to.
